          <h3>What platforms does Octopus support?</h3>
          <p>
            You can access Octopus from any modern browser on any platform through <a href="http://octopusmetrics.com">http://octopusmetrics.com</a>. To interface hardware devices and create recordings, you will need to install the <a href="#connector">Octopus Connector</a>, which is currently available for <a href="/connectors">Mac OS X</a>.
          </p>
          <h3>Can I use Octopus with Windows or Linux?</h3>
          <p>
            We currently support Windows and Linux using a command line interface for the <a href="#connector">Octopus Connector</a>. Your machine will also need to have a Bluetooth interface. If you would like to use Octopus from a Windows or Linux machine, <a href="/contactus">let us know</a>.
          </p>
            <h3>What devices does Octopus support?</h3>
